{"tid":1060600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元州邨宿舍老翁上吊+燒炭 送院不治","createTime":"2019-03-13T23:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T23:56:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8cbe9d26cf2cb95e6f46a3a660005a9dbf76d2a6","tid":1060600,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T23:28:32.000Z","msg":"長沙灣元州邨元康樓，凌晨2時23分，4樓一個長者宿舍單位發生火警，並冒出濃煙，鄰居發現報警。消防員破門入屋，開一條喉及出動一隊煙帽隊撲救，並疏散宿舍約6、7名男長者到地下，約22分鐘後將火救熄，並在單位救出一名昏迷老翁，送院搶救惜終於不治。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，上址是單身宿舍單位，67歲姓郭老翁早前兩次因病入院治療，早幾日出院返回內地，昨午3時才返家。警方發現單位一鐵盆有炭灰，同時老翁頸有傷痕，懷疑吊頸及燒炭自殺，火舌並燒著雜物引起火警。警方調查事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=b468dc32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190314/59366372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190314%2F59366372&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=96b7de5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190314%2F59366372&h=cb468bf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190314/59366372</a>"},{"pid":"cd320c8c114b062ced36dc57666eb2634440d905","tid":1060600,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T23:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚇鳩死其他老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5af7c3b34f12e10df6bab490